These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, australian, brazilian
1. the brazilian is on the left of the australian##1
2. the brazilian is between the argentine and the australian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | argentine | brazilian | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, musical, mystery
1. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | adventure | musical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, jazz, funk
1. the fan of jazz is between the fan of trance and the fan of funk##2
2. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | funk | jazz | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, cat, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | bird | frog | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, sprite
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking lemonade##2
2. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | fanta | sprite |

 #################################

 
